@name		pEAS3
@description pEAS3 is multi-user web application, designed for sending out emails to lists
@author		Kristaps Ledins <krysits@gmail.com>, <twitter.com/krysits>, <github.com/krysits>
@url		http://krysits.com/peas/
@license	See LICENSE and license-codeigniter files
@version 	3.0
@since 		July 6, 2004

This Software makes use of CodeIgniter web framework, HtmlArea textarea solution and PHPmailer.

Installation:
- copy all files to your Web server root
- modify application/config/database.php file to your MySQL database credentials
- create new MySQL database in your phpmyadmin interface, import install.sql script into the new database
- make application/cache and application/uploads folders writable
- open web browser to your web address, click on New User and fill the From correctly
- login with your new credentials in Login page